A popular Nigerian politician and former governor of Ekiti State, Ayodele Fayose recently shared pictures of the moment Peter Obi visited his residence in lagos state.
The pictures were posted on the official Twitter account of fayose. Below is the screen capture of the post;
While sharing the pictures on Twitter, he captioned the post below; “I met with my fellow PDP Presidential Aspirant, Peter Obi in my Lagos residence this evening. We both canvassed rotation of the Presidency to the South”.
Check out the pictures he posted below;
From the pictures that was shared above, you will clearly see Ayodele Fayose and Peter Obi having a good time.
However, as we expected just a few hours ago after the pictures went viral online, fans and followers raced down to the comments box section and reacted from a different perspective.
